sd = SideDict()
assert sd.max_price() is None
sd[Price('100.0')] = 1
sd[Price('99.99')] = 1
sd[Price('100.001')] = 1
sd[Price('100.01')] = 1
sd[Price('100.02')] = 1
assert sd.max_price() == Price('100.02')
del sd[Price('100.02')]
assert sd.max_price() == Price('100.01')
del sd[Price('100.0')]
assert sd.max_price() == Price('100.01')
del sd[Price('99.99')]
assert sd.max_price() == Price('100.01')
del sd[Price('100.01')]
assert sd.max_price() == Price('100.001')
del sd[Price('100.001')]
assert sd.max_price() is None
